<section>
  <h2 id="validation-recap">Validation Recap</h2>

  <p><strong>Where does validation of user-inputted data occur in the technology stack that we&#39;re using? In the datbase? The application?</strong> &#8594;</p>

  <p class="fragment">In our technology stack, validation occurs in the application layer - both on the client side and on the server side.</p>

  <p class="fragment"><strong>Should validation occur on the client, server, or both?</strong> &#8594;</p>

  <ul class="fragment">
    <li>minimally, it should be done on the server side since requests can originate from clients that aren&#39;t browsers</li>
    <li>ideally, validation would be done on both the server and client side</li>
  </ul>

  <p><br /></p>

  <p class="fragment"><strong>Where in our application have we done validation so far?</strong> &#8594;</p>

  <ul class="fragment">
    <li>in the mongoose Schema</li>
    <li>on the client side through form elements</li>
  </ul>

  <p><br /></p>

  <p class="fragment"><strong>Let&#39;s review some validation.</strong> &#8594; &#8230;  <strong>And&#8230; let&#39;s go back and check out other places where we can place validation.</strong> &#8594;</p>
</section>
